remarks.example:
Basic usage:

var client = new HighSpeedEServerClient();
client.Connect("192.168.1.100");
var status = client.GetStatusInformation();
var position = client.GetRobotCartesianPosition();
client.Close();

member.example:
Basic usage with High Speed Ethernet Server:

var robot = new YaskawaRobot();
robot.Connect("192.168.1.1");
var status = robot.HighSpeedEServer.GetStatusInformation();
Console.WriteLine($"Robot is in {status.Mode} mode");
robot.Disconnect();
